---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MainNavigation from '../components/MainNavigation';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | United Security Virginia" 
  description="Privacy policy for United Security Virginia. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our security services and website."
  type="website"
>
	<MainNavigation client:load />
	
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 via-gray-200 to-gray-300 overflow-hidden">
		<div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-header mb-6">
					Privacy Policy
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-header mb-8 leading-relaxed">
					Your privacy and data security are important to us
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Main Content -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">
					<strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 1, 2024
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					United Security Virginia ("we," "us," or "our") collects information from you when you use our website, request services, or interact with our company. The types of information we may collect include:
				</p>
				
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-header mb-3">Personal Information</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-header mb-6">
					<li>• Name, email address, phone number, and mailing address</li>
					<li>• Business information including company name and role</li>
					<li>• Service location addresses and property details</li>
					<li>• Communication preferences and service history</li>
				</ul>

				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-header mb-3">Technical Information</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-header mb-6">
					<li>• IP address, browser type, and device information</li>
					<li>• Website usage data and pages visited</li>
					<li>• Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-4">
					We use the information we collect for the following purposes:
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-header mb-6">
					<li>• Providing security services and customer support</li>
					<li>• Scheduling service appointments and installations</li>
					<li>• Communicating about your services and account</li>
					<li>• Improving our website and service offerings</li>
					<li>• Sending important security system notifications</li>
					<li>• Complying with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">3. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-4">
					We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information in the following limited circumstances:
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-header mb-6">
					<li>• With service providers who assist in our operations (equipment suppliers, monitoring services)</li>
					<li>• When required by law or to protect rights and safety</li>
					<li>• In connection with emergency response services</li>
					<li>• With your explicit consent for specific purposes</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide services, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements. Service records and customer information are typically retained for 7 years after service termination.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">6. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-4">
					You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-header mb-6">
					<li>• Access and review your personal information</li>
					<li>• Request corrections to inaccurate information</li>
					<li>• Opt out of marketing communications</li>
					<li>• Request deletion of your information (subject to legal requirements)</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">7. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to improve user experience, analyze website traffic, and provide personalized content. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">8. Third-Party Links</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites and encourage you to review their privacy policies.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Our services are not directed to individuals under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 18.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">10. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new policy on our website and updating the "Last Updated" date.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">11. Contact Information</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-4">
					If you have questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us:
				</p>
				<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
					<p class="text-lg text-header mb-2"><strong>United Security Virginia</strong></p>
					<p class="text-lg text-header mb-2">Phone: <a href="tel:540-989-9393" class="text-primary hover:underline">540-989-9393</a></p>
					<p class="text-lg text-header mb-2">Email: info@unitedsecurityva.com</p>
					<p class="text-lg text-header">Address: Southwest Virginia</p>
				</div>

				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-header mb-4">12. Virginia State Privacy Rights</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-header leading-relaxed mb-6">
					As a Virginia-based company serving Virginia residents, we comply with all applicable Virginia privacy laws and regulations. Virginia residents have additional rights under state law regarding their personal information.
				</p>

				<div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
					<p class="text-lg text-header">
						<strong>Questions or Concerns?</strong> If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your personal information, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="tel:540-989-9393" class="text-primary hover:underline">540-989-9393</a>.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<ContactSection client:load />
	<Footer client:load />
</Layout>